        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1949-09-29T20:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1949-09-29T20:00:00-05:00" n="1116" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1116">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">393.115/9–2949: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Consul at Shanghai</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">McConaughy</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-09-29T20:00:00-05:00">September 29, 1949—8 p. m.</date> 2003.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reurtel 4116, Sep 29. Pls keep Dept informed all available details Isbrandtsen
                    vessels, particularly geographical coordinates vessels <pb facs="1150" n="1140" xml:id="pg_1140"/> positions vicinity Tungsha buoy and any reported
                    movements from that area.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Webb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
